.TH "ccw_device_wait_idle" 9 "ccw_device_wait_idle" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ccw_device_wait_idle \- busy wait for device to become idle
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" ccw_device_wait_idle
.BI "(struct ccw_device *cdev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cdev" 12
ccw device
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Poll until activity control is zero, that is, no function or data
transfer is pending/active.
Called with device lock being held.
